    [Description]
        Trys to a cargo into the nearest vehicle to the cargo, handles feedback to player

    Arguments:
    0. <Object> cargo

    Return Value:
    <nil>

    Scope: Server
    Environment: Any
    Public: [Yes]
    Dependencies:

    Example: [_cargo] remoteExecCall ["A3A_Logistics_fnc_tryLoad",2];

